title: Desiigner Is Dropping A New Single Tomorrow
text:
Home > Music > Desiigner Is Dropping A New Single Tomorrow Desiigner Is Dropping A New Single Tomorrow 3 0 Posted by Trevor Smith   It's called "Outlet." 
Desiigner is ready to deliver the follow-up to "Tiimmy Turner." The GOOD Music rapper has announced that his new single, "Outlet," will premiere on Beats 1 radio tomorrow at 12PM EST. â€” Desiigner (@LifeOfDesiigner) February 8, 2017 
The single shares its name with Desiigner's first headlining tour, which he announced earlier this week . While the rapper's New English mixtape received a mixed reception, he has found success as a singles artist, with both "Panda" going 4x platinum and "Tiimy Turner" going platinum.
